@h1 Settings
This is the page to edit your personal information. Fill out/edit the following forms if you would like to create new/edit your account.
@dl
@dt First Name: 	
@dd
Enter your first name into this text field.
@dt Middle Name: 	
@dd
Enter your middle name into this text field.
@dt Last Name: 	
@dd
Enter your last name into this text field.
@dt List Size: 	
@dd
Click the drop menu to click the list size you wish to have whenever you see a list on this site.
@dt Time Zone:
@dd
Enter the time zone you are in ie. UTC 	
@dt User Id:
@dd
Enter the user ID you wish to use.
@dt Forum/Subscribed?
@dd
Click the check box to the according forum if you wish to subscribe to it.
@dt OK
@dd
Click OK to save
